WEBVTT

1
00:00:10.266 --> 00:00:11.400
Why are you here?

2
00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:12.866
Are you here to watch my humiliation?

3
00:00:13.133 --> 00:00:15.366
How dare you be disrespectful to Consort Rong!

4
00:00:15.800 --> 00:00:18.066
Minister, you go outside and wait.

5
00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:22.033
I need to speak with the consort alone.

6
00:00:23.333 --> 00:00:24.200
It's all your fault.

7
00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:26.366
It must be you, this enchanting consort, who stirred things up.

8
00:00:26.366 --> 00:00:29.466
Otherwise, the Emperor wouldn't be so harsh with me.

9
00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:31.066
I’m inciting discord?

10
00:00:31.700 --> 00:00:32.500
Hmph.

11
00:00:33.066 --> 00:00:36.233
When you were crying and insisting on seeing the Emperor last night,

12
00:00:36.666 --> 00:00:39.766
the Emperor was actually in my Changchun Palace.

13
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:43.233
If you hadn’t been confined to your palace,

14
00:00:43.266 --> 00:00:46.700
you would have been given the “childbearing soup” by now.

15
00:00:47.766 --> 00:00:49.166
If he argues with you,

16
00:00:49.166 --> 00:00:51.800
don’t worry, he won’t be able to bear it for long.

17
00:00:52.300 --> 00:00:54.133
Once he is favored by the Emperor,

18
00:00:54.133 --> 00:00:56.066
I will prepare the “childbearing soup” for him.

19
00:00:56.300 --> 00:00:58.300
If he becomes pregnant with the dragon’s seed,

20
00:00:58.466 --> 00:01:00.066
not only will he be pregnant,

21
00:01:00.266 --> 00:01:02.766
but he will also bleed excessively and die.

22
00:01:02.766 --> 00:01:04.766
If he doesn’t become pregnant with the dragon’s seed,

23
00:01:05.133 --> 00:01:08.333
he will lose his fertility forever.

24
00:01:08.333 --> 00:01:09.366
How would you know?

25
00:01:09.500 --> 00:01:11.366
How would I know?

26
00:01:12.366 --> 00:01:14.300
Because I am a witch.

27
00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:17.900
I am here today by the Empress Dowager’s order.

28
00:01:18.166 --> 00:01:20.666
But don’t worry, I won’t touch you.

29
00:01:28.166 --> 00:01:29.500
Wushan isn’t bad.

30
00:01:42.766 --> 00:01:45.333
In the last life, the Emperor was deceived by you.

31
00:01:45.333 --> 00:01:48.033
Fortunately, nothing happened that night.

32
00:01:48.133 --> 00:01:50.133
Otherwise, I would have died at your hands.

33
00:01:50.133 --> 00:01:51.366
Even so,

34
00:01:51.500 --> 00:01:53.066
I was still harmed by you,

35
00:01:53.500 --> 00:01:55.166
unable to have children again.

36
00:01:55.466 --> 00:01:56.766
What are you talking about?

37
00:01:56.766 --> 00:01:58.000
What previous life?

38
00:01:58.000 --> 00:01:59.566
In this life and the previous one,

39
00:02:00.300 --> 00:02:02.033
you want to kill me.

40
00:02:02.166 --> 00:02:04.400
How can I spare you?

41
00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:05.500
You’re insane.

42
00:02:05.500 --> 00:02:07.633
Your Majesty, Your Majesty, save me!
